      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Déterminer les réels $a$ et~$b$ tels que~:\n    $I(\\alpha) = \\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac a{b+n^2}$.",
        "html": "<p>Déterminer les réels <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(b\\)</span> tels que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I(\\alpha) = \\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac a{b+n^2}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
